 Font maker v1.3                                                  Page 2


 This utilitie was made to create fonts for DEGAS,  I have not been able to
test it with other programs, so I don't know how that performs.
 If you have questions about this program,  please  send me a letter,  with
an envelope with your own address and stamps to send it back included. My 
address is at the end of this document.
 I've tried to keep the use of the program as simple as posible.












































 Font maker v1.3                                                  Page 3


 Under the Menu-line you can find the following options:
SAVE                         : To save the font in a file that can be used
                               by DEGAS. Saving files sometimes cause errors,
                               I don't know why, so be carefull.
LOAD                         : To load an already existing font in DEGAS-
                               font.
ERASE                        : This is used to make the current character
                               empty (= Blank).
FILL                         : This function is the opposite of ERRASE, it
                               fills out the current character.
INVERT                       : Use  this  option  to  invert  the  current 
                               character.
JUMP TO CAHRACTER            : This can be used to make a character the 
                               current character, you are asked to give in
                               the number of the character, to jump to.
COPY                         : This command copies a character to an other
                               character.
SWAP                         : To exchange two characters.
QUIT                         : To stop, see to it you have saved the 
                               edited font.
 On the screen you can do the following:
EDIT                         : Simply move the mouse-cursor to the square
                               to be set/reset and click the left mouse-
                               button.
GOTO NEXT/PREVIOUS CHARACTER : Move the mouse-cursor in the box with the
                               option of you choice, and click the left
                               mouse-button. The 'cursor' now moves to the
                               next/previous character.
 The file created can directly be used by DEGAS. I hope you like this
handsome utility. If you do, please send me a contribution of about
HFl 15.-- or an equal amount of money in an other monetary unit. In 
anticipation, thank you very much.My address is :


